When I was over there I sleep on the ground

30
00:02:04,450 --> 00:02:06,810
拿石头当枕头  像原始人一样
and used rock for pillows, like a caveman.

31
00:02:06,890 --> 00:02:09,890
现在我回家了  躺在床上  就像...
Now I'm home, lying in my bed, and it's like...

32
00:02:09,890 --> 00:02:11,170
躺在棉花糖上
Lying on a marshmallow.

33
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:12,930
感觉自己快沉到地上去了
I feel like I'm gonna sink right to the floor.

34
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,130
多久
How long?

35
00:02:15,930 --> 00:02:16,860
两次派驻
Two tours.

36
