有多少海盗
How many pirates?

77
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:55,920
25个
Twenty-five,

78
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:59,420
顶级雇佣兵  由乔治·巴托克带领
top mercs, led by this guy. Georges Batroc.

79
00:03:59,770 --> 00:04:01,990
前对外安全总局行动部的
Ex-DGSE, Action Division.

80
00:04:01,990 --> 00:04:04,230
国际刑警"红色通缉令"头号通缉犯
He's at the top of Interpol's "red notice".

81
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:05,910
被法国遣散前
Before the French demobilized him,

82
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,590
他执行过36次击杀任务
he had thirty-six kill missions.

83
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:09,780
他就擅长大开杀戒
This guy's got a rep for maximum casualties.

84
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:10,520
人质呢
Hostages?

85
00:04:10,790 --> 00:04:11,930
大都是技术人员
Mostly techs.

86
00:04:12,100 --> 00:04:14,730
一名官员  贾斯珀·西特韦尔
One officer, Jasper Sitwell.

87
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:15,800
都在厨房
They're in the galley.

88
00:04:15,990 --> 00:04:17,640
西特韦尔在发射船上做什么
What's Sitwell doing on a launch ship?

89
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,490
好了  我搜索甲板  找到巴托克
Alright, I'm gonna sweep the deck and find Batroc.

90
00:04:19,490 --> 00:04:21,640
小娜  你关掉引擎等待命令
Nat, you'll kill the engines and wait for instructions.

91
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:24,320
朗姆洛  你负责船尾  找到人质
Rumlow, you sweep aft, find the hostages,

92
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:26,140
带他们上救生艇  救走他们  出发
get them to life pods. Get 'em out. Let's go.

93
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:27,920
突击队  听到了吧  准备行动
S.T.R.I.K.E, you heard the Captain. Gear up!

94
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,430
七频道确认安全
Secure channel seven.

95
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,560
确认
Seven secure.

96
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:45,510
周六晚上找乐子了吗
You do anything fun Saturday night?

97
