她可能会同意呢
she'll probably say yes.

102
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,470
所以我才不约
That's why I don't ask.

103
00:05:00,130 --> 00:05:02,120
太害羞还是太害怕
Too shy or too scared?

104
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:03,220
是太忙
Too busy!

105
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,610
他戴降落伞了吗
Was he wearing a parachute?

106
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,820
没有  没戴
No. No, he wasn't.

107
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:06,180
不要动  不要动
Don't move! Don't move!

108
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,220
谢谢
Thanks.

109
00:07:10,290 --> 00:07:12,410
不用谢  这不是看你没我挺无助的
Yeah. You seemed pretty helpless without me.

110
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:18,600
住你对门的护士怎么样
What about the nurse that lives across the hall from you?

111
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,710
她好像人不错
She seems kind of nice.

112
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:21,630
先搞定轮机舱  再给我做红娘
Secure the engine room, then find me a date.

113
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:23,060
我能一心多用
I'm multitasking.

114
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:27,550
我跟巴托克说了  想要神盾局付钱
I said to Batroc, if we want SHIELD to pay,

115
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:29,530
就得杀几个人给他们看
we have to start sending bodies now!

116
00:07:31,690 --> 00:07:33,850
我就准备杀一个
I have a bullet for someone.

117
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:36,070
你想吃枪子吗
You want a bullet in your head?!

118
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,200
收好腿  想吃枪子吗
Move that leg. Want a bullet in your head?

119
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:48,710
我不喜欢等
I don't like waiting.

120
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:51,800
打给杜兰德
Call Durand.

121
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:54,680
救援一来就开船
I want the ship ready to go as soon as the rescue arrives.

122
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:55,810
是  巴托克
Yes, Batroc.

123
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:04,140
杜兰德  启动引擎
Durand. Start the engine.

124
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:04,940
好
Okay.

125
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,290
你好  水手
Hey, sailor.

126
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:33,080
闭嘴  怎么回事  想当英雄吗
Shut up. What is it? Want to be a hero?

127
00:08:38,430 --> 00:08:40,420
我可等够了
Well, I've waited long enough.

128
00:08:44,050 --> 00:08:46,490
找巴托克
Hey, look for Batroc.

129
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,770
两分钟内不回话  我就开始杀人了
If I do not hear in two minutes, I'll start to kill them!

130
00:08:48,770 --> 00:08:50,340
好  我去找他
Okay. I'll find him!

131
00:08:59,430 --> 00:09:00,450
两分钟
Two minutes.

132
