巴托克  神盾局的没回应
Radio silence from S.H.I.E.L.D, Batroc.

133
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:39,700
目标确认
Targets acquired.

134
00:09:40,010 --> 00:09:41,260
突击队就位
S.T.R.I.K.E in position.

135
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,520
