Hey, you! Take the girl.

141
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,250
听我命令
On my mark.

142
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:30,090
三  二  一
Three. Two. One.

143
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:38,590
我说过  神盾局从不谈判
I told you, S.H.I.E.L.D doesn't negotiate.

144
