那边没回应  联系不上
the line is dead. I lost contact with them.

146
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:47,550
小心
Look out!

147
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:01,190
人质正在撤退
Hostages enroute to extraction.

148
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,540
罗曼诺夫没有来碰头  队长
Romanoff missed the rendezvous point, Captain.

149
00:11:05,170 --> 00:11:07,140
敌方仍在反抗
Hostiles are still in play.

150
00:11:07,450 --> 00:11:09,620
娜塔莎  巴托克逃了
Natasha, Batroc's on the move.

151
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:12,090
绕回朗姆洛那里  保护人质
Circle back to Rumlow and protect the hostages.

152
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:13,720
娜塔莎
Natasha!

153
00:11:50,450 --> 00:11:52,310
你不是光靠盾吧
I thought that you were more than just a shield.

154
00:12:06,330 --> 00:12:07,200
