What are you doing?

157
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,130
备份硬盘数据
Backing up the hard drive.

158
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,650
这是个好习惯
It's a good habit to get into.

159
00:12:43,410 --> 00:12:44,270
朗姆洛需要你帮忙
Rumlow needed your help.

160
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:45,520
你在这干什么呢
What the hell are you doing here?

161
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,710
你在挽救神盾局情报
You're saving S.H.I.E.L.D intel.

162
00:12:50,710 --> 00:12:51,980
